### VisionPulse AI V4 endpoint smoke tests
@base = http://localhost:5000/api

### Health
GET {{base}}/health

### Fast API status
GET {{base}}/ai/status

### Provider probe
GET {{base}}/ai/status?probe=true

### Assets
GET {{base}}/assets

### Assets with quotes
GET {{base}}/assets?live=true

### Silver strict quote check
GET {{base}}/market/quote/SILVER

### Gold strict quote check
GET {{base}}/market/quote/GOLD

### Multi-asset quote check
GET {{base}}/market/quotes?symbols=GOLD,SILVER,BTC,ETH,OIL,SPY,QQQ,NVDA

### Combined Live News + Smart Event Calendar feed
GET {{base}}/news?query=Trump%20speech%20Fed%20remarks%20CPI%20oil%20bitcoin%20gold%20market&pageSize=45

### Calendar/data events
GET {{base}}/events

### Generate calendar prediction
POST {{base}}/predictions/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "eventId": "evt_cpi_us_001",
  "assetSymbol": "GOLD"
}

### Generate custom news prediction
POST {{base}}/predictions/generate
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "assetSymbol": "BTC",
  "customEvent": {
    "id": "custom_test_trump_speech_market_watch",
    "title": "Trump speech / tariff comments market watch",
    "description": "Political remarks can move USD, gold, stocks, oil, and crypto if tariff or foreign policy language surprises markets.",
    "category": "geopolitical",
    "importance": "medium",
    "impactLevel": "medium",
    "assetHints": ["GOLD", "SPY", "QQQ", "BTC"],
    "affectedAssets": ["GOLD", "SPY", "QQQ", "BTC"],
    "source": { "name": "VisionPulse test news" },
    "publishedAt": "2026-04-28T20:00:00.000Z",
    "eventTime": "2026-04-28T20:00:00.000Z"
  }
}

### Reviews
GET {{base}}/reviews

### Review summary
GET {{base}}/reviews/summary
